Harms in his treatise makes this point relying on {\ul\ulc0 Nel v Silicon Smelters (Edms) Bpk} {\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s8{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs16\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 1981 4 SA 792(A) at 801-802}}}
